{"tid":1611263,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"終有一日，所有前線會全部陣亡","createTime":"2019-10-02T02:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:59:20.000Z","uid":62623,"like":59,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"395b7d2a4ca67513426917d756cbd9c772452638","tid":1611263,"uid":62623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:08:08.000Z","msg":"10.1開槍射人基本上傳達咗一條極度危險嘅信息：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警察殺人無後果</span><br />\n<br />\n高層攬到實一實，唔會有人因此而負責，開槍嘅人甚至變成英雄，俾著你係警察，開唔撚開槍？<br />\n<br />\n當開實彈變成常態，然後發展到亂槍掃射，所有前線勇武，甚至係後排和理非通通變槍下亡魂真係遲早嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我係對成個事態非常悲觀，因為香港人係一種和理非到連激進少少嘅反抗都唔肯嘅生物，就算有人死，第二日都係照常返工。大規模嘅麻包袋、對警狗用神獸呢啲更加係無可能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">俾我錯判一次好唔好？<br />\n今次輸咗，我地就天堂見㗎啦</span>"},{"pid":"08d2735092daa16da9f36a4741700bb5579b2ea6","tid":1611263,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:09:19.000Z","msg":"今日12點半，黑西裝癱瘓全中環！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uHbC1Eo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuHbC1Eo.jpg&h=4dc0bb16&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FM3BxL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFM3BxL4.jpg&h=2748d568&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y4xntjp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY4xntjp.jpg&h=a178f2c0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aeb62c5e117dae189a05685185e2791b8bb5a6b2","tid":1611263,"uid":117420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:10:40.000Z","msg":"SAD BUT TRUE"},{"pid":"f19358695d1c85087dceed5ff165afc20715ca20","tid":1611263,"uid":175168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:12:29.000Z","msg":"由前排有人開第一下真槍，已經知道日後會陸續咁開..<br />\n<br />\n10月1  射左第一次人，都可以無事<br />\n黎緊成個10月，